  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646710/extras/1138d93f9d56690a3cb2935ae6e25f0f.avif?t=1624975018\" width=512 height=71 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646710/extras/db5fe056628dc3ff6ff8a91d1e008c29.webp?t=1624975018\" width=514 height=10 /></span><br>Demon Cycle is a casual strategy game, where luck favors the prepared. You have limited turns to make enough coins to pass the floor. Your choices will determine the outcome.<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Tough choices with a dash of luck<br></li><li> Upgradeable Demon Minions<br></li><li> Over 50 unique cards<br></li><li> Give the Demon Lords exactly what they asked for.... maliciously~ <br></li><li> 5 Demon Lords to defeat and get Loot!<br></li><li> Campaign/Endless Mode</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646710/extras/8dc8a8b09efcb01b8e7d26992c2a8868.avif?t=1624975018\" width=512 height=300 /></span><br>This is a game created by two people, and has been an exciting endeavor! And we thank you for supporting us!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1646710/extras/246d11712a2fba159eed9a643bce85f6.webp?t=1624975018\" width=514 height=10 /></span>",
